OL,5, A modern slaver whose disabled victim  
OL,6, was exploited for 40 years has been    
OL,7, given a suspended prison sentence.     
OL,9,FPeter Swailes' victim was made to work 
OL,10,Fon farms for little pay and slept in a 
OL,11,Fshed, Carlisle Crown Court heard.      
OL,13,FSwailes admitted conspiring to         
OL,14,Ffacilitate travel of another with a    
OL,15,Fview to exploitation. His father, also 
OL,16,Fcalled Peter Swailes, 81, faced the    
OL,17,Fsame charge but died in 2021.          
OL,19,FSwailes, 56, was jailed for nine       
OL,20,Fmonths, suspended for 18 months.       
